                "description": "THE NATIONAL WEATHER SERVICE HAS ISSUED TORNADO WATCH 137 IN\nEFFECT UNTIL 11 PM CDT THIS EVENING FOR THE FOLLOWING AREAS\n\nIN OKLAHOMA THIS WATCH INCLUDES 17 COUNTIES\n\nIN CENTRAL OKLAHOMA\n\nCANADIAN              CLEVELAND             GRADY\nKINGFISHER            LOGAN                 MCCLAIN\nOKLAHOMA              PAYNE\n\nIN NORTHERN OKLAHOMA\n\nGARFIELD              GRANT                 KAY\nNOBLE\n\nIN NORTHWEST OKLAHOMA\n\nALFALFA               BLAINE                MAJOR\n\nIN SOUTHWEST OKLAHOMA\n\nCADDO                 COMANCHE\n\nTHIS INCLUDES THE CITIES OF ANADARKO, BLACKWELL, BLANCHARD,\nCARMEN, CHEROKEE, CHICKASHA, CONCHO, EL RENO, ENID, FAIRVIEW,\nGEARY, GUTHRIE, HELENA, HENNESSEY, HINTON, KINGFISHER, LAMONT,\nLAWTON, MEDFORD, MOORE, MUSTANG, NEWCASTLE, NORMAN, OKARCHE,\nOKEENE, OKLAHOMA CITY, PERRY, PONCA CITY, POND CREEK, PURCELL,\nSTILLWATER, TUTTLE, WAKITA, WATONGA, AND YUKON.",
